### Welcome to the busy team official page
we are a team of three students decided to do what we love best, 
developing android apps . 
***


### Main target 
Our main target is to develop useful apps that helps to make our users happy.
***


### On the road to success 
We have created a collection of different apps that showed a mixture
of relative success and terrible failure , it is funny but we know 
we are on the road . With more trying and maybe more failure we will
achieve success.    
***
